quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  100,1,"'uqsim allah taealaa balkhyl aljaryat fi sabilih nahw aledwwi, hin yuzhir swtha min sureat eadwiha. wala yajuz llmkhlwq 'an yuqsim 'iilaa ballh, fa'iina alqism bighayr allah shrk"
  100,2,falkhyl allaati tnqdh alnnar min salabat hwafrha; min shddat eadwha
  100,3,falmghyrat ealaa al'aeda' eind alsbh
  100,4,fhyajn bhdha aleadw ghbarana
  100,5,ftwssatn brkbanhn jmwe alaeda'
  100,6,"'in al'iinsan linem rabih lajhwd, wa'iinah bjhwdh dhlk lmqr. wa'iinah lihubi almal lshdyd"
  100,7,"'in al'iinsan linem rabih lajhwd, wa'iinah bjhwdh dhlk lmqr. wa'iinah lihubi almal lshdyd"
  100,8,"'in al'iinsan linem rabih lajhwd, wa'iinah bjhwdh dhlk lmqr. wa'iinah lihubi almal lshdyd"
  100,9,afla yaelam al'iinsan ma yantaziruh 'iidha 'akhraj allah al'amwat min alqubur llhsab waljza'?
  100,10,wastukhrj ma asttr fi alsudur min khayr 'aw shr
  100,11,"'in rabahum bihim wbaemalhm yawmayidh lkhbyr, la yakhfaa ealayh shay' min dhlk"